<div id="review_2100102380" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2100102380" />
    <a title="destiny ♡⚔♡ [howling libraries]" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/15335689-destiny-howling-libraries"><img alt="destiny ♡⚔♡ [howling libraries]" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1627172939p2/15335689.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2100102380?book_show_action=true">Aug 21, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="destiny ♡⚔♡ [howling libraries]" class="user" itemprop="url" name="destiny ♡⚔♡ [howling libraries]" href="/user/show/15335689-destiny-howling-libraries">destiny ♡⚔♡ [howling libraries]</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/15335689-destiny-howling-libraries?shelf=graphics">graphics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/15335689-destiny-howling-libraries?shelf=ya">ya</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/15335689-destiny-howling-libraries?shelf=review-copies">review-copies</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/15335689-destiny-howling-libraries?shelf=nonfic">nonfic</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/15335689-destiny-howling-libraries?shelf=tough-topics">tough-topics</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2100102380" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5754335066920140553">I went into this graphic novel knowing <i>nothing</i> about it; it was on the &quot;read now&quot; list on NetGalley, and I was in the mood for a quick graphic novel. (Joke&apos;s on me - this graphic novel is over 500 pages long!)<br/><br/>Essentially, <i>Lighter Than My Shadow</i> is a story about eating disorders, body dysmorphia, and sexual assault. It&apos;s a memoir in the form of a graphic novel, written to tell the story of Katie Green&apos;s own childhood and teen life. It&apos;s a very sad and haunting story, but unfortunately, it&apos;s just </span>
  <span id="freeText5754335066920140553" style="display:none">I went into this graphic novel knowing <i>nothing</i> about it; it was on the "read now" list on NetGalley, and I was in the mood for a quick graphic novel. (Joke's on me - this graphic novel is over 500 pages long!)<br /><br />Essentially, <i>Lighter Than My Shadow</i> is a story about eating disorders, body dysmorphia, and sexual assault. It's a memoir in the form of a graphic novel, written to tell the story of Katie Green's own childhood and teen life. It's a very sad and haunting story, but unfortunately, it's just not a very enjoyable read, either. It has incredibly slow pacing for a GN, which is unusual in my experience, and the scenes are <b>extremely</b> repetitive.<br /><br />If you're particularly fond of memoirs about mental illness, you may be interested in this title, but otherwise, I'd pass it up.</span>
  <a data-text-id="5754335066920140553" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


